9. The dielectric forming method of claim 8 and further wherein said plurality of sidewall-exposed material layers of the ONO-type memory cell stack include:
(b.3) a silicon layer;
(b.4) a tunnel dielectric layer;
(b.5) wherein the first silicon nitride layer is above the first silicon oxide layer; and
(b.6) wherein the combination of the first silicon oxide layer and the first silicon nitride layer is above the first silicon layer.
